getTransportFlags().Description: Returns flags with additional information about the backup transport. For supported flags see @B_android#app#backup#BackupAgent_E@

getQuota().Description: Returns the quota in bytes for the application's current backup operation. The value can vary for each operation.

ClassDesc: Provides the interface through which a @B_android#app#backup#BackupAgent_E@ writes entire files to a full backup data set, via its @B_android#app#backup#BackupAgent#onFullBackup_E@ method.
